description: Two Italians Deli & Pizzeria is the latest mobile food truck to hit Chicago. Our daily menu includes baked Italian pastries, cookies, fresh breads, rum cakes & much more.  We offer a full deli & pizzeria menu that delivers the best subs, sandwiches & salads right off our truck in the Chicago area, all with true Italian meats & cheeses.  At Two Italians food truck, we also offer a wide variety of deli meats, cheeses, olives, imported pastas & take-n-bake pizzas. Try us once & you’ll love our food. We guarantee it!
name: Two Italians
